layout: base.njk
permalink: /cli/
pageTitle: "Command Line"
tourSteps:
  - selector: ".terminal"
    title: "Same orchestrator, different surface"
    body: "Click any scenario on the right to watch the CLI in action. When you're done — that's the whole tour. <br><br>Real Hōzō ships with this, the web UI, ntfy/Pushover/SMTP notifications, WebAuthn auth, and a break-glass restore. <a class='underline text-blue-300' href='/about/'>How it got built →</a>"
---

<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">

  {# ── Left: terminal ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-head">
        <span class="dot r"></span>
        <span class="dot y"></span>
        <span class="dot g"></span>
        <span class="ml-2">~/hozo$</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body" id="term-body" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Terminal output"></div>
    </div>

    {# ── Controls ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mt-4">
      <button
        id="btn-next"
        class="px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm font-semibold btn-primary text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
        aria-label="Advance to next step"
      >▸ Next</button>

      <button
        id="btn-replay"
        class="px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm font-semibold bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-slate-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-400"
        aria-label="Replay current scenario from start"
      >↻ Replay</button>

      <button
        id="btn-skip"
        class="px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm font-semibold bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-slate-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-400"
        aria-label="Skip animation and show all output immediately"
      >⏭ Skip animation</button>
    </div>

    {# ── Explainer ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
    <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
      The <code class="text-slate-200 bg-slate-800 px-1 rounded">hozo</code> CLI
      mirrors the web UI 1:1. Anything you can do in the dashboard, you can
      script. The web UI is a thin layer over the same orchestration.
    </p>
  </div>

  {# ── Right: scenario sidebar ─────────────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div class="md:w-72 w-full">
    <div class="card p-4">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-3">Scenarios</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">

        <button
          data-scenario="help"
          class="text-left px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm font-mono bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
        >▸ Hello &amp; help<br><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-sans">hozo --help</span></button>

        <button
          data-scenario="list"
          class="text-left px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm font-mono bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
        >▸ List jobs<br><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-sans">hozo jobs list</span></button>

        <button
          data-scenario="run"
          class="text-left px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm font-mono bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
        >▸ Run a backup<br><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-sans">hozo jobs run nightly-rpool</span></button>

        <button
          data-scenario="status"
          class="text-left px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm font-mono bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
        >▸ Check remote status<br><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-sans">hozo status --job nightly-rpool</span></button>

        <button
          data-scenario="wake"
          class="text-left px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm font-mono bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
        >▸ Send WoL<br><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-sans">hozo wake nightly-rpool</span></button>

        <button
          data-scenario="shutdown"
          class="text-left px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm font-mono bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500"
        >▸ Shutdown remote<br><span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-sans">hozo shutdown nightly-rpool</span></button>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<script src="/assets/js/terminal.js"></script>
